name: John ARAGAO v. AMERICAN EMERY WHEEL WORKS

opinions.text:
ORDER
The motion of respondent American Emery Wheel Works to affirm the final decree of the Appellate Commission pursuant to Rule 16(g) is denied.
DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Lovett & Linder, Ltd., Lauren E. Jones, Providence, for petitioner.
Eldredge H. Henning, Jr., Providence, for respondent.
